        Selling Brisbane Property to a Foreign Buyer: FIRB, Surcharge Duty, and What It Means for Your Settlement
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Foreign buyers are a legitimate part of the Brisbane property market, but they come with specific approval requirements and additional acquisition costs that every seller should understand before signing a contract.
      </p>
